title: Cyber bullying : common types of bullying 2019 , by gender
summary: This grouped bar chart has 4 categories for the x axis of Response representing Male, and Female.
The highest category is found at I have been cyber bullied (lifetime) with a mean value of 36.4.
The second highest category is found at I have been cyber bullied (previous 30 days) with a mean value of 17.4.
